SABREWIN.INI
This is an initialization file. By editing this file, you can
have SABRE come up in different-sized windows. The "screen_height"
and "screen_width" parameters can be edited as desired. Note that
the larger the window, the slower the game will run due to the
increased number of pixels which must be generated. You can also
change the size of the window while the game is running
by dragging on the lower right corner.
 
KEYS
This version contains new key combinations. Please refer to the help 
topic "Keys Reference" for a guide
